General(-at-)OldVolks.com writes:
>   Thank you for the info. I couldn't figure it out. I am looking at 2 
> different hatchtops and the owners said there were SO 34, they both have 
> the same interior ( mosaic) and non flip seat. So it appears that both of 
> these hatch tops were ordered with a removable interior and not stationary. 
